        "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/bitcoin/bitcoin/contents/doc/gitian-building.md?ref=99fda26de0661afcbe43d5e862c382e3c2e3aa5e",
        "patch": "@@ -262,12 +262,12 @@ Then set up LXC and the rest with the following, which is a complex jumble of se\n # the version of lxc-start in Debian 7.4 needs to run as root, so make sure\n # that the build script can execute it without providing a password\n echo \"%sudo ALL=NOPASSWD: /usr/bin/lxc-start\" > /etc/sudoers.d/gitian-lxc\n-# add cgroup for LXC\n-echo \"cgroup  /sys/fs/cgroup  cgroup  defaults  0   0\" >> /etc/fstab\n # make /etc/rc.local script that sets up bridge between guest and host\n echo '#!/bin/sh -e' > /etc/rc.local\n echo 'brctl addbr br0' >> /etc/rc.local\n echo 'ifconfig br0 10.0.3.2/24 up' >> /etc/rc.local\n+echo 'iptables -t nat -A POSTROUTING -o eth0 -j MASQUERADE' >> /etc/rc.local\n+echo 'echo 1 > /proc/sys/net/ipv4/ip_forward' >> /etc/rc.local\n echo 'exit 0' >> /etc/rc.local\n # make sure that USE_LXC is always set when logging in as debian,\n # and configure LXC IP addresses"
      }
    ]
